Add To Every object
  Verb throw
  End Verb throw.
End Add To.

The l1 Isa location
  Verb throw
    Does Only
      "You can not throw anything in here."
  End Verb.
  Exit e,w,s,n To l2.
End The l1.

The l2 Isa location
  Exit e,w,s,n To l1.
End The l2.

The hero
  Container
End The hero.

The ball Isa object
  In hero
  Verb throw
    Does "You throw the ball."
  End Verb.
End The ball.

Start At l1.
  "Throw the ball. Then go east to l2 and throw it there."

